---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = "Privacy Policy | KPOP Idol Chemistry";
const description = "Privacy policy for KPOP Idol Chemistry K-Pop name generator. Learn how we handle your data.";
const lastUpdated = "December 2025";
---

<BaseLayout 
  title={title} 
  description={description}
  keywords={["privacy policy", "kpop name generator privacy"]}
>
  <div class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      
      <section>
        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          Welcome to KPOP Idol Chemistry ("we," "our," or "us"). We respect your privacy 
          and are committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy explains 
          how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our K-Pop name 
          generator service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3>2.1 Information You Provide</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Name Input:</strong> The name you enter for generating K-Pop names. This is processed locally in your browser and is not stored on our servers.</li>
          <li><strong>Contact Information:</strong> If you contact us via email, we collect your email address and message content.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>2.2 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> We use Google Analytics to collect anonymous usage statistics such as page views, time spent on site, and general location (country/region).</li>
          <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Browser type, device type, and screen resolution for optimizing user experience.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>2.3 Local Storage</h3>
        <p>
          We store the following data locally on your device (not on our servers):
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Generation history and favorites</li>
          <li>Level progress and badges</li>
          <li>Theme preferences</li>
          <li>Statistics (for your personal view only)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide and improve our K-Pop name generator service</li>
          <li>Understand how users interact with our website</li>
          <li>Respond to your inquiries and support requests</li>
          <li>Display relevant advertisements through Google AdSense</li>
          <li>Prevent fraud and ensure security</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <h3>4.1 Google Analytics</h3>
        <p>
          We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors use our site. Google Analytics 
          collects information anonymously and reports website trends without identifying 
          individual visitors. You can opt out of Google Analytics by installing the 
          <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.
        </p>

        <h3>4.2 Google AdSense</h3>
        <p>
          We use Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google uses cookies to serve ads 
          based on your prior visits to our website or other websites. You can opt out of 
          personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Ads Settings</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>5. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          We use cookies and similar technologies for:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Remembering your preferences (theme, language)</li>
          <li>Analytics (Google Analytics cookies)</li>
          <li>Advertising (Google AdSense cookies)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          You can control cookies through your browser settings. Note that disabling cookies 
          may affect some features of our website.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We implement appropriate security measures to protect your information. However, 
          no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure. We cannot guarantee 
          absolute security of your data.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our service is intended for users of all ages. We do not knowingly collect 
          personal information from children under 13 without parental consent. If you 
          believe we have collected information from a child under 13, please contact us.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
          <li>Request data portability</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Since we don't store personal data on our servers (only locally on your device), 
          you can clear your local data by clearing your browser's local storage for our site.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any 
          changes by posting the new policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at:
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:idplife35@gmail.com">idplife35@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: 40px 0;
  }

  .legal-page .container {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .legal-page h1 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .last-updated {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  section h2 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding-bottom: 8px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
  }

  section h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text);
    margin: 16px 0 8px;
  }

  section p {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  section ul {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-left: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  section li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  section li strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  a {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    section h2 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
  }
</style>

